.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── Ingested data ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTE: books/ and db/ are intentionally committed so they deploy to Render
# (the free tier has ephemeral disk — anything not in the repo is lost on restart).
# Only the per-user accounts DB and rendered page-image cache stay out of git.
db/users.db
static/book_images/

# ── Python ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
